# Cloudflare Pages headers for predictorsleague.co.uk
# HSTS makes browsers auto-upgrade http -> https internally after the first
# visit, skipping the ~0.8s redirect hop on later loads. Scoped to the apex
# host ONLY: intentionally no `includeSubDomains` (so it can't force-HTTPS a
# subdomain that isn't ready) and no `preload` (the hard-to-reverse part).
# 1-year max-age matches the WC app's existing HSTS. Safe: the apex is
# HTTPS-only and already serving over TLS.
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000
